{"tid":381352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人夫非禮人妻？ 2對支那夫婦排隊變毆鬥","createTime":"2017-08-31T00:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T02:50:09.000Z","uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b049c4c9a017e4bfdd92b80da801b99be6faa6d4","tid":381352,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:36:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170830/57148630\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170830%2F57148630&d=IUd5jLMePWSn6jkrzwc9WDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=945e499f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170830%2F57148630&h=516308c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170830/57148630</a><br />\n<br />\n香港國際機場發生支那遊客群毆事件！據現場消息稱，事發在下午1時許，有數名支那遊客在支那東方航空櫃台對開排隊，準備辦理登機手續，惟其間白衫男指灰衫男排隊時非禮其妻子(身穿粉紅色T恤)，眾人初則口角，繼而動武。<br />\n<br />\n據目擊者形容，起初白衫男不斷毆打灰衫男，親友幫忙阻止不果。按現場拍攝到的片段可見，灰衫男其後亦有還擊，更將白衫男的T恤亦扯爛，而白衫男的「粉紅tee」妻子亦加入戰圈，一直扯著灰衫男的頭髮，但對方不甘示弱，兜巴摑向白衫男，之後二人拳來拳往，另灰衫男的妻子(灰色外套)亦上前幫手，再演變成男女子分開對戰，最後由旁人報警處理。<br />\n一直處於下風的灰衫夫婦，捱打了逾1分鐘，灰衫女更以支那話向旁人投訴：「警察為甚麼還不來，我老公被他們打死了！」有目擊者亦回應說：「叫一下警察。」直至片尾，終見有兩名機場職員出現，其中一人幫忙勸交。"},{"pid":"c2972f803f9fda619d3e1f66fa94e6721f84ec51","tid":381352,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:43:50.000Z","msg":"混雙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63df4cb23b3fff8c9faa15c85b428a2b36bc114b","tid":381352,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:46:36.000Z","msg":"唔知點解睇到交尾"},{"pid":"ffb0351e18c2f0f4a8a40f42d6bda1380e74d902","tid":381352,"uid":36152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:50:26.000Z","msg":"報咩警，等佢地打下先.....<br />\n強國J帶特色...<br />\n<br />\nPS:以前做J公司地勤見得太多"},{"pid":"34d2455e744002a1581a765a167d3b0e68b266fd","tid":381352,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:53:19.000Z","msg":"特警溝緊女，邊得閒理你"},{"pid":"2ff62a7a57dd9956fea300da0fc5c51454364d73","tid":381352,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:05:41.000Z","msg":"屌，咁都摸得落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebb8e895ed2a66b4fb1e27eedd0d0b409b68cca","tid":381352,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T02:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}